node.text:
That’s an official wrap on Plus/Minus ❤️ these beautiful people mean so much to me, an Instagram caption could never do them justice.
Thank you @netflix for allowing us to play and trusting me as your leading lady and executive producer. I can’t wait for you all to see what we put our hearts into this summer 🌸➕➖
